{"tid":2291093,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［周梓樂死因研訊］警方間接承認令周梓樂延誤送院","createTime":"2020-11-18T13:28:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T13:37:58.000Z","uid":188515,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"38445e15b5e38827c1f9a725f6fd0ef1a6aeded4","tid":2291093,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:28:23.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】科大學生周梓樂死因研訊繼續，代表周梓樂父母的大律師質疑當晚有消防車因車路被擋要折返，警方指當時要專注掃蕩。<br />\n代表周梓樂父母的大律師質疑，警方向停車場發射催淚彈可能有火警風險。曾經帶領小隊進入停車場掃蕩的指揮官黃家倫指，當時指示警員向停車場二樓至三樓方向發射催淚彈，應落在行人路近泊車位，撞到車輛的機會微乎其微。<br />\n律師又追問當晚有消防車到達現場後，因車路被擋要沿路折返、有否考慮傷者可能因同一情況得不到適切的醫學治療？黃家倫指，<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"large\">當時有更高層次考慮，要專注掃蕩、消除前方潛在的危險威脅</span></span>，讓傷者可在安全環境下得到救援。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ott-news.i-cable.com/zh-hk/l/open-content?cid=40270&amp;ct=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fott-news.i-cable.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fl%2Fopen-content%3Fcid%3D40270%26ct%3D1&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5puyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=bc10988f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ott-news.i-cable.com/zh-hk/l/open-content?cid=40270&amp;ct=1</a>"},{"pid":"8da893abe78c75db33fd2e0507efafc4f42581b4","tid":2291093,"uid":124983,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:29:30.000Z","msg":"警察死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75403db2e7570a0025b102cd7c12e3c419f27c58","tid":2291093,"uid":188515,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:29:47.000Z","msg":"毋忘手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sf6Y9y-_fjY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fsf6Y9y-_fjY&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5puyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=dd7df52c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sf6Y9y-_fjY</a>"},{"pid":"14be5a18935013de682cd8c658aa73b14d7110e6","tid":2291093,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T13:30:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pi